      "message": "IIUC, this is the base path for `cmd[0]`. However, the doc of `cmd` only says that it is relative to the cipd pkg root but doesn\u0027t mention about user payload. I\u0027m thinking should we move this field inside `Executable` message to make the cohesive fields stay together? Or are you intentionally placing them in different places to hide it from user as it is only needed in led?",
